item.title: Bowled over by Tenpin
item.author: Jessica Chan,
item.description: Having already achieved impressive 13.5-2.5 and 9-7 victories over Southampton and last year runners-up Portsmouth, Imperial Tenpin Bowling has had a promising start to the year.
